{"tid":1574043,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"浸中爆左校長門冇人講！？","createTime":"2019-09-16T08:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T09:09:10.000Z","uid":261330,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a56af22e4333a8c049775bbad64f317195178801","tid":1574043,"uid":261330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T08:53:29.000Z","msg":"浸中終於可以做返浸大了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚（15日）有浸大學生記者於北角被捕，有同學今午發起行動，要求校長錢大康承諾支援被捕學生及譴責警方濫權濫捕。學生遊行至逸夫行政樓，宣讀聲明之後，部分人直接前往八樓要求與錢大康會面。<br />\n<br />\n上到八樓之後，大門鎖上，於是有學生爆門進入八樓範圍。學生起初撬門鉸，後來有人帶來磚頭，擊破大門玻璃，破門而入。玻璃碎片散落一地，亦有人用噴漆塗污閉路電視鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n浸大副校長周偉立從校長室出來，表示錢大康目前外出開會，他會致電予錢大康。現場學生表示，會留守至錢大康與他們會面。"},{"pid":"4e01fdfc020c711384bb8c540e13d205bfef00bd","tid":1574043,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T08:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wBfJ3Kt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwBfJ3Kt.jpg&h=035c3ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=713bfe8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=a9b003e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/suck.withyo